en_983351_0	A workshop 'Beauty Culture' was organised for women in military families and all woman soldiers, resident in 21 Division area and civilians living in Anuradhapura on 28 July.
en_983351_1	The programme was facilitated by one of the veteran beauticians, Ms Surangi Kodithuwakku by conducting lectures.
en_983351_2	In addition, all participants for this workshop were gifted with a set of beauty culture packs, sponsored by Off Marks PVT Ltd.
en_983351_3	The chief guest of the event was the General Officer Commanding of 21 Division Major General Kumar Jayapathirana.
en_983351_4	Senior Officers, Officers of the 21 Division and under command formations participated in the event.
